
** Proxyserver

Disabling the proxy server needs an reboot.

** User and SU

  - The user should be added to the wheel group

** Building Emacs GTK

  - xorg-x11-devel
  - gtk2_devel
  - libjpeg-devel
  - libtiff-devel
  - libpng-devel
  - giflib-devel
  
  - Fix /usr/X116/lib/X11/app-defaults/Emacs: missing comma

** Workspace

Add the program "Arbeitsbereichumschalter" to the control bar. 

Verify in the gconf-editor the option "/apps/metacity/general/num_workspaces".


** Oracle Installation

*** 11g

- 2 Warning, 1 Error (if DHCP)

*** Oracle Groups

  - dba
  - disk

*** Oracle EM

  - https://hostname:1158/em

*** Oracle Ports

  - 1521
  - 1158

